<title>Lal Na Sem Zing Hitiu</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ni lopi lenkawl en ding a nai tai,
 Chamna Lengmang leh tatsa lungtuok te'n;
 Thangvan zawlah khuong leh baza gi tawh,
 Ei sam unau tatsa guol deihte'n.

[V2]
 Gel zing un ni lopi,
 Kiguong zosa a umin;
 Thangvan laituola leng dingin,
 Lalpa na sem zing hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Malai Noah damlai gel zing unla,
 Ngailo in nuoi simlei hi nungsawn un;
 Hung mang intin, I buolnau gam lui hi,
 Namtin Jordan luigal kai tan au.

[V4]
 3. I lungtup gam ninnuom a hungtun tieng,
 Leia telchuomte laituol lengta ding;
 Kipahna tuoilo in zie gam achun,
 Tatsate laituol ah leng tai tui.

[V5]
 4. Leia A telchuomte'n gel zing unla,
 Zie gam lopi hung tunna ding ni chu;
 Lal zosieh Lal leh Lengmang chungnung chu,
 Chawian hitiu I Lal Krista chu.</lyrics>
</song>